Priority: optional
Maintainer: Roberto G. Valenti <robertogl.valenti@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0), ros-foxy-ament-cmake, ros-foxy-geometry-msgs, ros-foxy-message-filters, ros-foxy-rclcpp, ros-foxy-sensor-msgs, ros-foxy-std-msgs, ros-foxy-tf2, ros-foxy-ros-workspace
